(1, 'About Us', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(250, 32, 31);"><img height="28" width="175" alt="" src="/userfiles/image/about_us.png" /></strong>\r\n<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />\r\n<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">\r\n<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">Think Groupon meets Ebay meets Etrade.<br />\r\nCurrenTcy is a Chicago-based technology company with a vision to revolutionize the online deal marketplace.&nbsp; The currenTcy is innovative way business can interact with consumers.&nbsp; We have combined the thrilling elements of a &lsquo;stock market&rsquo; with &lsquo;on-line deals&rsquo; and &lsquo;social commerce&rsquo; creating a dynamic marketplace where prices on deals fluctuate based on &lsquo;real-time&rsquo; consumption and purchasing behavior of the public.&nbsp; The currenTcy is much more than a daily deal site or any deal site for that matter.&nbsp;&nbsp; It is an interactive deal marketplace where consumers can take advantage of favorable market conditions.&nbsp; Business can instantaneously create a &lsquo;buzz&rsquo; and drive in &lsquo;real-time&rsquo; traffic at the whim of the business owner wanting to offer incredibly deep discounts to be used by a certain time (perhaps even that night)!<br />\r\nMy mom is so nice</meta>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
