(8, 'FAQ', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img height="29" width="69" src="/userfiles/image/faq.png" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>test</p>\r\n<p>josh</p>\r\n<p>jesse</p>\r\n<p>adam</p>'),
(9, 'How it works for Consumer', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(250, 32, 31);"><img height="30" width="268" src="/userfiles/image/how_it_works.png" alt="" /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Buy Low, Spend High!</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Start playing the currenTcy deal market today!&nbsp; It&rsquo;s a simple, interactive, innovative, and an extremely fun way to purchase deals in your neighborhood.&nbsp; Watch the prices of deals go up and down in &lsquo;real-time&rsquo; and purchase them when you think the time is right!&nbsp; Set up an account for FREE and start playing.&nbsp; Remember -- Buy Low, and Spend High!&nbsp; </p>'),
(10, 'How it works for Business', '<p style="padding-top: 5px; text-align: center;"><strong style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(250, 32, 31);"><img height="30" width="268" alt="" src="/userfiles/image/how_it_works.png" /><br />\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Create an Instant Buzz.&nbsp; Generate ''real-time'' Business.&nbsp; Play.&nbsp; Win.<br />\r\n</strong>A revolutionary way to generate business and attract new and old customers!&nbsp; Instantly post deals to the public&hellip;you are in complete control! Select the deal value, starting price, increase and decrease parameters, use by date, deal details, and much more.&nbsp; Create a &lsquo;real-time&rsquo; buzz and drive instant traffic to your business by posting an incredible deal that must be used by a certain date - perhaps even tonight!&nbsp; Start playing today &ndash; you have nothing to lose and everything to gain!<br />\r\nSimply create a FREE acount and start posting deals today.&nbsp; After you register your account, your business will go through a validation and approval process (it may take up to 48 hours to become an approved business). Once approved by the currenTcy, LLC, you can start posting live deals to the currenTcy marketplace.<br />\r\nYou are in complete control of your deal.&nbsp; Post one anytime.&nbsp; De-activate it anytime.&nbsp; Set up all the parameters including the deal value, starting price, use by date &amp; time, increase parameters, decrease parameters, deal ceiling &amp; floor prices, and more...<br />\r\nWhen a consumer purchases a deal, they recieve a unique code to redeem at your place of business.&nbsp; When a customer comes to redeem the deal, simply log into your business account and validate the secret code (you can always validate it later, if you are certain the deal hasn''t been validated yet -- no one, including you, ever knows the secret code except that buyer).<br />\r\nWhen you validate the deal, it will update both your and the consumer records. <br />\r\nBefore you can start posting live deals to the currenTcy, you will first have to become an approaved and verified business</p>');
